  • Method Details

    • acceptApplication

      public void acceptApplication​(pruefungsvorbereitung.Application application, Office location)
      Accepts the given application and assigns the developer to the office provided. Updates the cash of the studio accordingly.
      Parameters:
      application - pruefungsvorbereitung.Application to accept
      location - Location to assign to
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - If location is unknown
      IllegalStateException - If the studio does not have enough cash

    • acceptProject

      public void acceptProject​(Project project, List<Developer> developers)
      Accepts the given project and assigns it to the developers to work on

      The developers must not work on a project already and must be located in the same office.

      Parameters:
      project - Project to accept
      developers - Developers to assign to
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - If the developers are already assigned to a project or not in the same office
